data.description: Introducing your dream home! This gorgeous 1-story home in the coveted Grove at Bull Creek neighborhood is move-in ready and waiting for you. Features: • Spacious and open layout for seamless living. • Perfect for entertaining with vinyl floors in main areas. • Cozy carpet in the bedrooms for comfort. • Open concept kitchen with built-in microwave, large pantry, granite countertops, and a center island for gatherings. • Builder Warranty for peace of mind, ensuring top-quality craftsmanship. • Energy Efficiency: Save on bills with energy-efficient windows and a smart home thermostat. • Conveniently located with quick access to US 79 and just minutes from HEB, Walmart, and restaurants. • Plus, you’re just minutes away from the new Samsung facility. Don’t miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this beautiful home yours! Schedule a showing and seize the chance to experience the Grove at Bull Creek lifestyle.
